WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
A young seal rests on the wet sand by the sea.

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
Its spotted body slides slowly, leaving a trail behind it.

00:06.000 --> 00:08.000
The sound of waves accompanies its calm movement.

00:08.000 --> 00:10.000
It looks towards the horizon, curious, before continuing its way to the water.
